            <div type="section" xml:id="Legislation">
                <head>Legislation</head>
                <p>There is no legislation governing the access to diplomatic archives.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Location">
                <head>Location</head>
                <p>Ministry of Foreign Affairs: PO Box 103, Gyalyong Tshokhang, Thimphu, Bhutan</p>
                <p>National Library and Archives of Bhutan: GPO PO Box 185, Kawangjangtsa, Thimphu,
                    Bhutan.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="section" xml:id="Procedures">
                <head> Procedures</head>
                <p> Researchers should contact the Ministry of Foreign Affairs directly to inquire
                    about access to diplomatic records.</p>
            </div>
